Your customer has 60,000 users on a dedicated SAN that wish to migrate to Exchange
2010 on a virtualized SAN environment with HP 3PAR StoreServ. The 140,000 user HP
3PAR StoreServconfigurationusing the Microsoft Exchange Solution Reviewed Program
framework required 28 SAN Fabric Fiber Channel ports. How many Fiber channel ports will
your customer need?
A. Six Fiber channel ports
B. Eight fiber channel ports
C. Ten fiber channel ports
D. Twelve fiber channel ports
Answer: D
Your customer has a number of servers with dedicated storage running windows
applications. Which software is designed specifically for virtualized environment with HP
3PAR StoreServ 7000?
A. HP 3PAR StoreServ Security Suite
B. HP 3PAR StoreServ Application Suite for VMware
C. HP 3PAR StoreServ Data Optimization Suite
D. HP 3PAR StoreServ Application Suite for Exchange
Answer: C
